 w∧←~,(newwords∊⊂,'*')∨(¯3↑¨newwords)∊⊂'(*)' ⍝ Preserve special cases as always-keyword
 :If ∨/t←'⍎'∊¨w/,newwords ⋄ (t/w/,newwords)←(t/w/,newwords)~¨'⍎' ⋄ w←w\~t ⋄ :EndIf
